==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''resilience'''
# the [[mental]] [[ability]] to [[recover]] [[quickly]] from [[depression]], [[illness]] or [[misfortune]]
# the [[physical]] property of  [[material]] that can [[resume]] its [[shape]] after being [[stretched]] or [[deformed]]; [[elasticity]]
# the ability of a [[system]] or [[company]] to [[recover]] from a [[catastrophic]] [[failure]] caused by [[power]] [[outage]], a [[fire]], a [[bomb]] or similar (particularly [[IT]] systems, [[archive]]s)

